## 🚀 How to Run

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/market-data-visualizer.git
```

2. Navigate to the project directory:

```bash
cd market-data-visualizer
```

3. Start a local web server:

```bash
npx serve
```

4. Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:3000).

5. Upload a CSV file containing OHLC market data to begin visualizing the chart.
